<HEADLINE> Beatles Fans Gather in Liverpool </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LIVERPOOL, England (AP) -- Thousands of fans gathered in the  
Beatles' hometown Monday to celebrate the re-issue of ``Yellow 
Submarine,'' the 1968 cinematic landmark of Beatlemania. 
