was hit in the neck and grazed in the left hand, and a 48-year-old 
person had several gunshots wounds to the neck, cheek, arm, thigh 
and buttocks, said a hospital spokeswoman. 
</P>
<P>
	A 15-year-old boy was shot in the ankle and was in good  
condition. 
</P>
<P>
	Garden Grove is about 35 miles southeast of Los Angeles.  
  	   	
