<HEADLINE> Father, Daughter Attacked in Ill. </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	CHICAGO (AP) -- A man who told police he was having ``a bad day''  
was charged with attempted murder in an attack in which two people 
were beaten with a wooden table leg. 
</P>
<P>
	The victims, a father and daughter who were assaulted while they  
and other family members headed to a White Sox game Saturday, were 
in critical condition today. 
</P>
<P>
	The attack took place across a street from a police station.  
</P>
