brother of beating victim Roy Trumblay. 
</P>
<P>
	Roy Trumblay, 56, and daughter Christine Trumblay, 22, both of  
the southwest suburb of Burbank, were both in critical condition 
today following brain surgery at Cook County Hospital. Roy 
Trumblay's wife, Gerr, and his daughter's boyfriend, Brian Quan, 
suffered less serious injuries in the attack, family members said. 
  	   	
