<HEADLINE> Pavarotti Settles Tax Evasion Probe </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	MANNHEIM, Germany (AP) -- Star tenor Luciano Pavarotti has paid a  
six-figure sum as part of a settlement in a German tax evasion 
probe, prosecutors said today. 
</P>
<P>
	Pavarotti, who toured the country with Placido Domingo and Jose  
Carreras, had been named in a tax evasion probe against German 
concert promoter Matthias Hoffmann. 
</P>
