the probe after he agreed to pay an undisclosed sum. Carreras' case 
remains open, prosecutors said. 
</P>
<P>
	Hoffmann was charged with funneling huge sums of money for the  
stars and himself to mailbox companies outside Germany. 
</P>
<P>
	A Mannheim court convicted him in December of evading taxes on  
$8 million of income and sentenced him to nearly six years in 
prison. He is free on bail pending an appeal. 
  	   	
