<TEXT>
<P>
	CINCINNATI (AP) -- The Cincinnati Bengals waived backup  
quarterback Eric Kresser, fullback Clif Groce and offensive lineman 
Rob Murphy on Monday. To reach the 65-player limit, the Bengals 
also designated two players as injured. 
</P>
