<CATEGORY> international </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE>  East Timorese Vote on Independence </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	DILI, Indonesia (AP) -- Throngs of East Timorese defied threats  
of violence to cast their ballots today in a U.N.-supervised 
referendum on independence after decades of Indonesian rule. 
</P>
<P>
	U.N. officials hailed the huge, peaceful turnout. They estimated  
